          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χρή</span></b>  (act. of <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χράομαι</span>): impers., <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">there is
            need</span>, w. acc. of person and gen. of thing, <i><span class="en">Od. 1.124</span></i>; then, one <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">must, ought,
            should</span>, w. acc. and inf. (either or both), <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">οὑδέ τί σε χρή</span>, ‘it behooves thee not,’ <i><span class="en">Od. 19.500</span></i>, etc.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
